= 서브플롯

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

x = np.linspace(0, 2 * np.pi, 100)
y_sin = np.sin(x)
y_cos = np.cos(x)

fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(10, 4))

axes[0].plot(x, y_sin)
axes[0].set_title("사인 함수")
axes[0].set_xlabel("X")
axes[0].set_ylabel("Y")

axes[1].plot(x, y_cos, color='orange')
axes[1].set_title("코사인 함수")
axes[1].set_xlabel("X")
axes[1].set_ylabel("Y")

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
```

